metadata.name: Moment #1
metadata.description:
***

My first work in this collection

In it, an ordinary guy decided to make a stop for the sake of a short, but very influential moment for his future life

***

This collection contains works that are dedicated to the moments in our life with you for which you can stop. Is it nature, architecture or other cute moments

***

Edition 1/1
6250x7813 | 150 ppi
Hand-drawn, edited in Adobe Illustrator
